ﺪاس ْﺳِﻷ ﺎًﻤﺎﺳ ْ أﺧ َبَﺮَﺿ
 
To be in a whirlwind of confusion; to be unable to think straight; at sixes and 
sevens; to be confused or puzzled. In Classical Arabic: to deceive. 
